  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is served every morning with both hot and cold options. For supper you'll have a delicious three-course meal from the daily à la carte menu in one of the hotels two restaurants. Your meal will go perfectly with a bottle of wine from the hotels enormous wine selection.</p>
<p>The hotel also offers a free aperitivo once a week where you'll be treated to a drink of your choice and a selection of local snacks.</p>
<p>For mountain picnics or a day-time snack, packed lunches are available for €10 per person (payable locally). These include a sandwich, a piece of fruit, a sweet snack and a soft drink or water. These can be requested at reception.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
